<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>اَلْمُسْتَحِقُّونَ لِلثُّمُن<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>اَلْمُسْتَحِقُّونَ لِلثُّمُنِ الزَّوْجَة<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>شُرُوطُ اِسْتِحْقَاقِ الزَّوْجَةِ لِلثُّمُن<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{وَلَهُنَّ الرُّبُعُ مِمَّا تَرَكْتُمْ إِنْ لَمْ يَكُنْ لَكُمْ وَلَدٌ , فَإِنْ كَانَ لَكُمْ وَلَدٌ فَلَهُنَّ الثُّمُنُ مِمَّا تَرَكْتُمْ}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) [النساء/١٢]</p> </div>